{
  "texts": [
    "To deal with this issue, multiple categories of sensors in different frequency bands, such as radar, Lidar, and camera should be integrated for cooperative sensing, facilitating the paradigm shift from the single-modal ISAC to multi-modal ISAC.",
    "Nevertheless, these senors are governed by different principles, and operate at different frequencies, and their sensing data are in distinct formats, making the effective data fusion and cooperation challenging.",
    "Fortunately, AI not only extracts the core features of multi-modal data but also achieves the effective fusion of these features for further analysis and processing, making AI-enabled multi-modal ISAC an emerging research direction.",
    "Lin et al. [275] investigated the multi-modal ISACbased environment reconstruction problem and proposed a multi-modal fusion network to combine the ISAC data and video data.",
    "In particular, their network first extracted the features of ISAC data and video data, and then leveraged a fusion module to combine the extracted features."
  ]
}